*Ubiću* te ako izdaješ moje ime. (I'll kill you if you betray my name.)

*Ubiću* ga ukoliko se ne pridržava pravila. (I'll kill him if he doesn't follow the rules.)

*Ubio* sam zmiju koja je napala moga psa. (I killed the snake that attacked my dog.) 

*Ubila* je gmaz koji je napadao njenu luku. (She killed the reptile that was attacking her cabbage.)

*Ubićemo* sve neprijateljske vojnike ako pokušaju da napadnu naš grad. (We'll kill all the enemy soldiers if they attempt to attack our city.)